FBIS3-27456 "drchi037_l_94005" FBIS-CHI-94-037 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Feb 1994 Science & Technology Beijing Sets Up Maritime Signals Satellite Station OW2302023494 Beijing XINHUA in English 0221 GMT 23 Feb 94 OW2302023494 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, February 23 (XINHUA) -- The Beijing Maritime Signals Satellite Ground Station, the only one of its kind so far in the country, passed tests here Tuesday [22 February]. In its trial operation the station handled nearly 200,000 domestic phone and fax calls, and 100,000 international calls. The station will improve links among mobile telecommunications systems users in the Pacific and Indian Oceans and users of stationary equipment on land.
